432
00:48:42,168 --> 00:48:46,668
Why shouldn't I believe the same in you?

433
00:48:46,668 --> 00:48:50,168
You may say I'm a fool

434
00:48:50,168 --> 00:48:54,168
Feelin' the way that I do

435
